Supplies found at the East-delf and the West-delf should be destroyed in order to lessen the strength of your foes within the Wildwood.
Destroy supply crates at the East-delf and West-delf
Supply crates can be found at the East-delf and the West-delf in the Wildwood.\n\nYou should destroy supply crates at the East-delf and the West-delf.
Foes of the Free Peoples are keeping supplies at the mine entrances of the East-delf and the West-delf within the Wildwood. Destroying these supplies should lessen the strength of foes here.
